          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="floating-badge badge-top">
        <div class="badge-icon">📍</div>
        <div class="badge-text">
          <strong>Salvador, BA</strong>
          <span>Evento presencial</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="floating-badge badge-bottom">
        <div class="badge-icon">🏆</div>
        <div class="badge-text">
